===================================   Step 01   ========================================
============================  Download and Install Python ===============================

Past this link to chrome and python.org will downloaded.
https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.12.4/python-3.12.4-amd64.exe
Now Install it (very easy)


===================================   Step 02   ========================================
========================  Download and Install VS code =================================

1. paste this link to your chrome and downloading will be started automatically for (Windows).
For Windows:  https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/?dv=win64user
For Mac:      https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/?dv=osx



===================================   Step 03   ========================================
=============================  Extensions for VS code ==================================

Open VS code and install these 2 extensions  in the side bar (extensions)
1. Code Runner
2. Python
